      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "諦めないわよ！　ページ数も削る気ないから\nここで諦めたら、編集部になんて言えばいいのよ",
      "startTime": 14.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.3492065747
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "バナナの皮で滑って転んで\n利き手の指を全部突き指したと素直に言うしか……",
      "startTime": 20.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
